## ğŸ¯ Project Objectives
- Design a **star schema** data model (fact and dimension tables).  
- Clean and normalize data using **Python (Pandas)**.  
- Load data into **BigQuery** and run SQL-based analysis.  
- Identify patterns of **editorial profitability** and **genre trends** over time.

